kjv_def: amaze, be (make) astonished, be beside self (selves), bewitch, wonder
strongs_def: to put (stand) out of wits, i.e. astound, or (reflexively) become astounded, insane
outline:
1. to throw out of position, displace
    1. to amaze, to astonish, throw into wonderment
    2. to be amazed, astounded
    3. to be out of one's mind, besides one's self, insane
